-- Vitol Negotiates With U.K. Authorities on Back Taxes: Times
-- B y   T h o m a s   B i e s h e u v e l
-- 2012-12-30T15:29:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-30/vitol-negotiates-with-u-k-authorities-on-back-taxes-times.html
Vitol Group has opened negotiations
after Her Majesty’s Revenue & Customs demanded back taxes, the
Sunday Times reported. * Vitol’s case involves use of an
offshore employee benefit trust * Vitol Chief Executive Officer
Ian Taylor says “We will have to pay something. We will work
hard to do what is best for our employees, but we must abide by
the legislation,” newspaper reports * HMRC declines to comment
on case, Sunday Times reports  To contact the reporter on this story:
Thomas Biesheuvel in London at 
 tbiesheuvel@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
